dialogue.name: senpai
dialogue.string: Is that my microphone? How the hell did you get that?

dialogue.name: senpai
dialogue.string: and what is that WORM doing here?!

dialogue.name: senpai
dialogue.string: Didn't have enough fun making a fool of me last time you showed up?

dialogue.name: senpai
dialogue.string: Now you're bringing more of your hideously attractive friends here to mock me once again?

dialogue.name: senpai
dialogue.string: You. Give me that back. I have another score to settle.

dialogue.name: monika
dialogue.string: Huh? No, wait, I was just about to-
